<para id="element-21">We must realize following characteristics of the static friction from the discussion so far :
</para>
<para id="element-22">
<list id="list-2" list-type="bulleted"><item> So long the body does not start moving, the static friction is equal to the component of net external force  in the direction parallel to contact surface. 
  </item>
<item> So long the body does not start moving, the static friction is a self adjusting force i.e. it varies with net external force in the direction parallel to contact surface. 
 </item>
</list>
</para>
<para id="element-23">Also, we must realize that friction force (
